Package: wigglescout
Title: Explore and Visualize Genomics BigWig Data
Version: 0.13.4
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Carmen",
           family = "Navarro",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "carmen.navarro@scilifelab.se"
           )
Description: A set of tools to easily extract, summarize and visualize
coverage on bigWig files genome-wide or in a locus-specific way. 
